Package fr.ens.biologie.generic

Interface DataContainer

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
public interface DataContainer extends Cloneable

An interface for objects that contain data.

Objects implementing this interface are assumed to contain data of an identical elementary type (Object or primitive types). The interface only deals with the block data treatments (clone, clear, fill...).

All fillWith(...) method have a default implementation that does nothing.
